{
  "stem": "11472.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have to tell you, my uncles, my mother's brothers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father and my uncle Nisel-- I have to say that he was really the leader.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my uncle Shulim, and my father, and they were very-- and my Uncle Sam was a young, little boy, but they were very able men.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had such imagination.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we came into this grotto, and there's no water in the grotto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people without water can't live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we would take pots or cans and put them near the rocks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And water would drip in, you know, and we would get those drippings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had problems with cooking, because they-- the smoke would back up on us, although the grotto was very big.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So one day, my uncle Nisel came back-- and the men were still free.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They did not come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would just come at night and bring us provisions, food, and then go back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were still free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They still had horses and wagons, and they were still free.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They came back and they said, my uncle Nisel really said it, that he's afraid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he spoke to my uncle Shulim, that he thinks that we should make another exit in this grotto-- dig up and look to try to make another exit in case they come in from the front.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That we should have another exit to escape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we should try to make in the grotto bunkers, so when they-- police and the Germans-- come, that the guide wouldn't know about those places.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So what happened, they start opening, they dug in, and they made-- they dug through, and they found some other-- you know, place that was not on the map.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no name on it, that nobody ever knew about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
